00:00:00.340 --> 00:00:05.270
So, now you understand a bit about
the alternate models of care delivery.

00:00:05.270 --> 00:00:07.640
But you may be asking,
why does this matter?

00:00:08.740 --> 00:00:12.710
For the answers to that, we turn again
to Marla to explore some of the serious

00:00:12.710 --> 00:00:15.270
problems facing US healthcare.

00:00:15.270 --> 00:00:18.360
This will set the stage for
understanding the key role that

00:00:18.360 --> 00:00:21.950
health IT may play in improving
our healthcare system.

